  "title": "Customer Service Officer | Jurong East - YZ11",
  "description": "<p><strong>Customer Service Officer</strong></p><ul><li>Working Hours: Monday - Friday (8am-5.30pm)</li><li>Location: Teban Garden - Jurong East</li><li>Salary : $2500 - $2800 </li><li>With AWS & Variable Bonus</li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Manage inbound and outbound calls, emails, live chats, and other digital communication channels, ensuring all interactions are accurately logged in the CRM system.</li><li>Handle and resolve customer complaints promptly, escalating issues when necessary and tracking Voice of Customer (VOC) feedback to improve service quality.</li><li>Provide coaching and support to retail agents through regular training sessions, maintaining updated SOPs and onboarding materials.</li><li>Monitor key performance indicators such as Customer Satisfaction Score (CSAT) and average handling time, prepare performance reports, and leverage insights to enhance service standards.</li><li>Ensure strict compliance with PDPA and internal data privacy policies, maintain accurate records, and support audit requirements.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>With relevant working experience </li><li>Min Diploma </li></ul><p><br />Tan Yen Zhen (Chen Yan Zhen) Reg No: R25138932</p><p>The SupremeHR Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</p>",
